  2. Ui7-tioh8 Ka-ki7 Thak8. 
  Lan2 teh thak8 Seng3-keng tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 niu5-a2 teh chiah8 sng-chai5-chhiu7-hioh8 e5 khoan2. Tu2-chiah chhut nng7 e5 niu5-a2, chin soe3-be2 ou-phu2-sek. Na2 chiah8 sng-chai5-chhiu7-hioh8, chiu7 chiam7-chiam7 toa7 be2 pian3 peh8-sek, au7-lai5 sin-the2 pian3 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 thau3-beng5 e5 khoan2, sim7-chi3 thou3-chhut sui2-sui2 e5 si. Thak8 Seng3-keng na7 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 thak8, ia7 beh chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni. In-ui7 Seng3-keng si7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7, m7-na7 oe7 hou7 lan2 e5 leng5-seng3 tiong2-toa7, koh oe7 hou7 lan2 tit-tioh8 chheng-khi3 e5 chok-iong7. Chu2 kong2: ¡§TaN lin2 in-ui7 Goa2 sou2 ka7 lin2 kong2 e5 to7-li2 i2-keng chheng-khi3 lah.¡¨ (Iok-han7 15:3).¡§Siau3-lian5 lang5 tioh8 eng7 sim2-mih8 lai5 chheng-khi3 i e5 sou2-kiaN5? Si7 tioh8 chiau3 Li2 e5 oe7 lai5 soe3-ji7 kiaN5¡¨ (Si-phian 119:9). Sou2-i2 lan2 na7 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 thak8 Seng3-keng, Seng3 Sin5 e5 kong-chok beh hou7 lan2 chhin-chhiuN7 niu5-a2 e5 khoan2, m7-na7 leng5-seng3 tiong2-chin3, na2-ku2 na2 seng3-kiat, hoat-kng, koh oe7 thou3-chhut si lai5 li7-ek pat8-lang5. 
  Bat u7 chit8-ui7 hak8-hau7 e5 kau3-oan5 lai5 tui3 goa2 tau5 i hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 tai7-chi3. Lian5-siok8 lai5 tau5 kui2-na7 pai2. U7 chit8-cha2-khi2 chin cha2 lai5 chhe7 goa2, mng7 khoaN3 thang kap i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 li7-hun a2-bo5? Hit si5, goa2 hut-jian5 siuN7-khi2 chit-ui7 hiaN-ti7 boe7 thang thun-lun2 tek-seng3, kiam2-chhai2 si7 bo5 teh thak8 Seng3-keng ki5-to2, sou2-i2 khiam3-kheh lek8-liong7. Sou2-i2 goa2 mng7 i mui2 cha2-khi2 u7 teh leng5-siu a2-bo5? Cha2-khi2 u7 thak8 Seng3-keng a2-bo5? I kong2 u7. Goa2 mng7 i cha2-khi2 thak8 to2-ui7 e5 Seng3-keng. I kong2, thak8 kau3 Chim-gian5 te7 14 chiuN.
  Goa2 koh mng7 i thak8-liau2 u7 tit-tioh8 sim2-mih8 ka3-si7 a2-bo5? I kong2 thak8-tioh8 hit ku3 ¡§So3-seng3 e5, toa7 hian2 gu5-gong7¡¨, put-chi2 u7 sou2 kam2-kak. I kong2 che tu2-tu2 si7 i hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 khoan2-sit. Goa2 ka7 i kong2: ¡§HiaN-ti7 ah, li2 thak8 Seng3-keng, si7 ui7-tioh8 li2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 teh thak8, bo5 ui7 ka-ki7 thak8, an2-ni, tui3 li2 bo5 li7-ek.¡¨ U7 chit8-pai2, ti7 goa2 kang2-to7 liau2 e5 si5, liam5-piN u7 chit8-ui7 chi2-be7 lai5 chhe7 goa2, ka7 goa2 kong2: ¡§E7-pou e5 kang2-to7 chin ho2, chin hah8 bou2-lang5 thiaN, chin kho2-sioh, e7-pou khoaN3 i long2 bo5 lai5 chu7-hoe7.¡¨ U7 loa7-choe7 lang5 thiaN kang2-to7, si7 teh ui7-tioh8 pat8-lang5 thiaN, kan-ta teh chu3-i3 ¡§chit ku3 hah8 sim2-mih8 hiaN thiaN, hit-ku3 hah8 sim2-mih8 che2 thiaN, ¡¨thoe3 pat8-lang5 thiaN-kau3 chin bo5 eng5, chong2-si7 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 khiok bo5 thiaN poaN3-ku3, sit8-chai7 chin kho2-sioh. Bat u7 chit8-ui7 bok8-su siu7 chhiaN2 khi3 chit8-keng kau3-hoe7 chu2-li2 le2-pai3. Hit-jit8 in-ui7 hong-hou7 chin-toa7, sui-jian5 kong3-cheng liau2, lai5 le2-pai3 e5 lang5 chi2-u7 chit8-ui7 na7-tiaN7. Bok8-su pun2-lai5 siuN7 m7 ku2-heng5 le2-pai3, chong2-si7 koh siuN7 to3-tng2, siuN7 kong2 tioh8 choe3 Chu2 tiong-sim e5 lou5-pok8, sou2-i2 chiu7 chiuN7 kang2-tai5 teng2, chhin-chhiuN7 teh chhoa7 hoe7-chiong3 le2-pai3 e5 khoan2, chiau3 i sou2 pi7-pan7 e5, chhoa7 hit-ui7 hiaN-ti7 choe3 le2-pai3, le2-pai3 soah e5 si5, hit-ui7 hiaN-ti7 ka7 bok8-su kong2: ¡§Bok8-su ah, cha2-khi2 li2 e5 kang2-to7 toa7-toa7 chhi3-chhak8 goa2 e5 sim. I2-cheng5 goa2 lai5 le2-pai3, long2 siuN7 kong2 tai5-teng2 e5 kang2-to7 si7 tui3 tai7-ke teh kong2, na7-si7 cha2-khi2 kan-ta goa2 chit8-e5 teh thiaN to7-li2 na7-tiaN7, sou2-i2 chiu7 siuN7 kong2 cha2-khi2 li2 sou2 kong2 e5, long2 si7 teh tui3 goa2 kong2--e5, sou2-i2 goa2 e5 sim siu7 chhi3-chhak8. TaN goa2 i2-au7 beh hoe2-kai2, choe3 tiong-sit8 e5 Ki-tok-tou5.¡¨ Chit-ui7 hiaN-ti7 i2-cheng5 long2 si7 ui7-tioh8 hoe7-chiong3 teh thiaN to7-li2, sou2-i2 ka-ki7 bo5 tit-tioh8 pang-chan7. Ti7 chit-pai2 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 thiaN to7-li2 e5 si5, pun2-sin chiah tit-tioh8 li7-ek. Sou2-i2 bo5-lun7 thak8 Seng3-keng a2-si7 thiaN kang2-to7, long2 tioh8 ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 thak8, ui7-tioh8 ka-ki7 thiaN, chiah u7 li7-ek. 
  3. M7-thang In-ui7 Thak8-liau2 Khoai3 Boe7 Ki3-tit Chiu7 Bo5 Thak8 
  U7 lang5 kong2 i thak8 Seng3-keng bo5 chhai2-kang, in-ui7 thak8-liau2 chin khoai3 boe7-ki3-tit, ui7-tioh8 an2-ni soa3 theng5-chi2 bo5 koh ke3-siok8 thak8. Seng3-keng na7 si7 siok8-leng5 e5 chiah8-mih8, chiu7 thak8 liau2 boe7-ki3-tit, ia7 si7 u7 li7-ek, m7-thang kong2 bo5 chhai2-kang. Chhi3-siuN7, li2 iau2-ku2 oe7 ki3-tit ti7 chit8 le2-pai3 cheng5 sou2 chiah8--e5, si7 sim2-mih8 mih8-kiaN7 a2-bo5? Ti7 chit8 le2-pai3 cheng5 e5 kin-a2-jit8, li2 phoe3 kui2-hang7 chhai3? Si7 phoe3-sim2-mih8 chhai3? Kiam2-chhai2 li2 i2-keng siuN7 boe7 chhut-lai5, chong2-si7 lan2 tiong-kan peng3 bo5 lang5 in-ui7 gau5 boe7-ki3-tit ka-ki7 sou2 chiah8 e5 si7 sim2-mih8 mih8, chiu7 theng5-chi2 bo5 beh ke3-siok8 chiah8. Lan2 tak8-jit8 sou2 chiah8 e5 mih8, sui-jian5 chin khoai3 boe7-ki3-tit, lan2 iu5-goan5 si7 ke3-siok8 beh chiah8, in-ui7 sui-jian5 gau5 boe7-ki3-tit, it-tan3 na7 u7 chiah8-loh8--khi3, chong2-si7 tui3 lan2 e5 sin-the2 u7 li7-ek, siau-hoa3 i2-au7, oe7 chiaN5-choe3 lan2 sin-the2 e5 lek8-liong7. Thak8 Seng3-keng e5 cheng5-heng5 ia7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni. Li2 eng7 ki5-to2 sou2 thak8 e5 Seng3-keng, u7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 kong-chok, tek-khak chiaN5 choe3 li2 leng5-seng3 siong7 e5 chu-iong2, chiaN5-choe3 li2 siok8-leng5 e5 khui3-lat8.
  Chiau3 chit8-poaN Ki-tok-tou5 e5 keng-giam7, peng5-si5 sou2 thak8 e5 Seng3-keng chhin-chhiuN7 chin gau5 boe7-ki3-tit e5 khoan2, chong2-si7 it-tan3 na7 tu2-tioh8 khiam3-eng7 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 e5 si5, u7 chin ki5-biau7 e5 hian7-siong7, chiu7-si7 oe7 eng3 hit-si5 e5 khiam3-eng7, siuN7-chhut Siong7-te3 e5 oe7. Che si7 Chu2 bat eng3-un2 e5 su7, Chu2 kong2 che si7 Seng3 Sin5 sou2 choe3 e5 kang. ¡§Na7 si7 Po2-hui7-su chiu7-si7 Seng3-Sin5, Pe7 ti7 goa2 e5 mia5 sou2 beh chhe e5, I beh chiong it-chhe3 e5 su7 ka3-si7 lin2, koh beh hou7 lin2 ki3-tit (Tiong-bun5 e5 hoan-ek8 si7 ¡§siuN7-khi2¡¨) goa2 it-chhe3 sou2 ka7 lin2 kong2 e5.¡¨ (Iok-han7 14:26) 
  U7 chit8-pai2 goa2 tui3 Hok-kian3 e5 Ko-phou2 chhiaN3 chit8-chiah sio2-chun5 beh khi3 Au7-khoe. Ke3-chiN5 kong2 ho2-se3 i2-au7, goan2 chiu7 chhut-hoat. Chong2-si7 chun5 sai2 kau3 TaiN3-chaiN5 (sou2-chai7 mia5), hit e5 ko3-chun5 e5 lang5 chiu7 kio3 goa2 chiu7 an2-ni chiuN7 hoaN7. Goa2 ka7 i kong2, goa2 si7 beh Au7-khoe, na7-si7 i bian2-kiong2 goa2 eng7 kiaN5 lou7 khi3, in-ui7 chi2-u7 chiaN5-li2-lou7 na7-tiaN7. Goa2 kong2, goa2 u7 toa3 heng5-li2, kiaN5-lou7 bo5 li7-pian7, koh goa2 kap i iok, si7 kau3 Au7-khoe, m7-si7 kau3 TaiN3-chaiN5. I kong2 koh khi2-khi3 hit cham7, chui2 lau5 khah kip kan-khou2 ko3, ia7 jit8-thau5 teh beh loh8-soaN, kiaN-liau2 i beh to3-khi3 Ko-phou2 siuN am3. Goa2 sit8-chai7 bo5 goan7-i3 koaN7 heng5-li2 kiaN5-lou7, goa2 ia7 bo5 hoaN-hi2 ko3-chun5 e5 lang5 bo5 chiau3 iok kiaN5. Ti7 hit-si5, hut-jian5 ti7 goa2 e5 sim-lai7 phu5-chhut chit8-chat Seng3-keng e5 oe7, chiu7-si7 Chu2 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7: ¡§Na7 u7 lang5 bian2-kiong2 li2 kiaN5 chit8 li2, chiu7 tioh8 kap i kiaN5 nng7 li2.¡¨ (Ma2-thai3 5:41) Tng Seng3 Sin5 hou7 goa2 siuN7-khi2 chit ku3 oe7 e5 si5, goa2 liam5-piN chiu7 chin hoaN-hi2 koaN7 heng5-li2 chiuN7 hoaN7. 
  Peng5-si5 chhin-chhiuN7 boe7-ki3-tit e5 khoan2, chong2-si7 ti7 su-iau3 e5 si5, Seng3 Sin5 oe7 hou7 lan2 siuN7-khi2 Chu2 e5 oe7. Sou2-i2 thak8 Seng3-keng gau5 boe7-ki3-tit, m7-bian2 hoe-sim, m7-thang theng5-chi2 bo5 thak8. 
  4. M7-thang Sim2-phoaN3 Seng3-keng 
  Tng Chu2 Ia5-sou khia7 ti7 chong2-tok Pi2-liap8-to e5 bin7-cheng5 siu7 khong3-ko3 siu7 sim2-mng7 e5 si5, ¡§Chu2 Ia5-sou bo5 in3 i chit8-ku3 oe7, ti3-kau3 chong2-tok toa7 ki5-koai3.¡¨ (Ma2-thai3 27:14) Peng5-siong5-si5 lan2 khoaN3-kiN3 Chu2 si7 un-jiu5 khiam-sun3, hou7 lang5 ho2 chhin-kun7. U7 si5 Chu2 Ia5-sou kang2-to7 soah, chin ia3-sian7, hak8-seng mng7 i boe7-beng5 e5 tai7-chi3, Chu2 it-it siong5-se3 soat-beng5 hou7 in thiaN. Ti7 bo5 eng5 e5 si5, choe3 lau7-bu2 e5 lang5 chhoa7 gin2-na2 lai5 beh kiu5 Ia5-sou ka7 in chiok-hok. Chu2 Ia5-sou ia7 it-it chhin-chhiat chiap-thai7 hiah e5 gin2-na2. Siang7 chit chit8-ui7 Ia5-sou, ti7 Pi2-liap8-to e5 bin7-cheng5 khiok koaiN-chhui3 m7 in3-tap, ti3-kau3 Pi2-liap8-to toa7 ki5-koai3. Che si7 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3? Chiu7-si7 in-ui7 Pi2-liap8-to khia7 ti7 sim2-phoaN3 e5 te7-ui7 teh mng7 Ia5-sou. Bo5-lun7 siaN2-lang5 na7 eng7 sim2-phoaN3 e5 thai7-tou7 tui3-thai7 Ia5-sou, Chu2 Ia5-sou long2 beh ng3 i cheng7-bek8 m7 in3-tap. Sou2-i2 thak8 Seng3-keng e5 si5, na7 u7 chun5 pheng5-phoaN3 e5 sim lai5 thak8, thak8 ia7 bo5 chhai2-kang, m7-na7 bo5 li7-ek hoan2-tng2 u7 sun2-hai7.
  5. Tioh8 Sin3-hok8 Siong7-te3 e5 Oe7 
  U7 chit8-ui7 se-kau3-su7 kong2: ¡§Lin2 Tiong-kok lang5 teh thak8 Seng3-keng e5 thai7-tou7 chin-ho2. Na2 thak8 na2 teh thim3-thau5.¡¨ (In-ui7 Tiong-bun5 e5 Seng3-keng si7 sia2 tit8-choa7, thak8 e5 si5 tui3 teng2-bin7 khoaN3 loh8 e7-bin7, chhin-chhiuN7 teh thim3-thau5 e5 khoan2.) I koh kong2: ¡§Goan2 goa7-kok lang5 thak8 Seng3-keng e5 thai7-tou7 chin m7-ho2,na2 thak8 na2 io5-thau5.¡¨ (In-ui7 Eng-bun5 e5 Seng3-keng si7 sia2 hoaiN5-choa7, thak8 e5 si5 tui3 to3-peng5 khoaN3-kau3 chiaN3-peng5, chhin-chhiuN7 teh io5-thau5 e5 khoan2.) I an2-ni kong2, si7 teh kong2 chhio3. Ti7 Tai5-oan5,sou2 teh eng7 Peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 Seng3-keng, ia7 si7 sia2 hoaiN5-choa7 e5, chong2-si7 lan2 e5 goa7-bin7 sui-jian5 io5-thau5, sim-lai7 khiok tioh8 thim3-thau5.¡§Tioh8 sin3-hok8 Siong7-te3 e5 oe7!¡¨ 
  U7 lang5 cho7 chit8-e5 kou3-su7, kong2 u7 chit8-e5 sin-phai3 e5 sin5-hak8-hau7, ti7 siong7-kho3 ka3 Seng3-keng e5 si5, hoan-hu3 hak8-seng long2 tioh8 oe7-ki3-tit toa3 ka-to lai5. Ti7 siong7-kho3, kau3-siu7 kang2-kai2 Seng3-keng e5 si5, na7 hoat-hian7 bo5 hap8 li2-ti3, bo5 hap8 kho-hak8 e5 pou7-hun7, thang eng7 ka-to ka7 i ka khi2--lai5, ka7 i san-tu5. Kiat-ko2, chiong Seng3-keng long2 cha-oan5 chit8-pian3 liau2-au7, chi2-u7 ka chhun 2 tiuN na7-tiaN7, chiu7-si7 chi2-u7 chhun 2 tiuN Seng3-keng phe5. Che si7 teh hong2-chhi3 sin phai3 sin5-hak8 e5 kou3-su7. I3-su3 si7 kong2 tui3 Seng3-keng na7 u7 khng3 giau5-gi5, chiu7 choan5-pun2 e5 Seng3-keng long2 beh chiaN5 choe3 gi5-bun7, sin3 boe7 loh8. 
  Na7-si7 an2-ni, Seng3-keng tiong hiah e5 boe7 thang liau2-kai2 e5 pou7-hun7 beh chaiN2-iuN7 chhu2-li2 nih? Tok8-tok8 sin3-hok8 Seng3-keng e5 oe7, in-ui7 Seng3-keng long2 si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 bek8-si7 e5! (II The5-mou5-thai3 3:16). U7 chit8-chat Seng3-keng pang-chan7 goa2 tui3 Seng3-keng m7-kaN2 khng3 giau5-gi5. Chiu7-si7 Pi2-tek hou7-su te7 3 chiuN te7 8 chat, kong2: ¡§HiaN-ti7 ah, u7 chit8-hang7 lin2 m7-thang boe7-ki3-tit, chiu7-si7 Chu2 khoaN3 chit8-jit8 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-chheng ni5, chit8-chheng ni5 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-jit8. ¡¨ Chu2 khoaN3 lan2 e5 chit8-chheng ni5 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-jit8! Chu2 na7 khoaN3 lan2 e5 chit8-chheng ni5 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8-jit8, an2-ni, Chu2 khoaN3 lan2 sou2 teh kong2 e5 ¡§jin5-seng 50 ni5¡¨si7 loa7-ku2? Put-ko3 si7 1 tiam2 koh 12 hun-cheng na7-tiaN7! Lan2 kong2¡§Jin5-seng 50 ni5¡¨, Chu2 kong2 ¡§Jin5-seng si7 1 tiam2 koh 12 hun-cheng.¡¨ OaN7 ku3 oe7 kong2, chit8-e5 i2-keng 50 he3 e5 lang5, kiam2-chhai2 i2-keng choe3 a-kong lah, keng-giam7 choe7 lah, na7-si7 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bak8-chiu tiong si7 chhin-chhiuN7 lan2 teh khoaN3 chit8-e5 tu2 chhut-si3 1 tiam2 12 hun-cheng e5 eN-a2 chit8-iuN7. Chit e5 su-siong2, po2-siu2 goa2 khiam-pi m7-kaN2 giau5-gi5 Seng3-keng e5 oe7.
  Ti7 chia na7 u7 chit8-e5 gou7, lak8-he3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 thiaN lang5 kong2 ¡§Sia7-hoe7 chu2-gi7¡¨ chit e5 beng5-su5 chiu7 lai5 mng7 lau7-pe7 khoaN3 ¡§Sia7-hoe7 chu2-gi7¡¨ si7 sim2-mih8 i3-su3, lau7-pe7 chai-iaN2 gin2-na2 e5 li2-kai2-lek8 iau2 bo5 kau3-giah8 thang beng5-pek8, chit-khoan2 e5 soat-beng5, chiu7 chi2-u7 oe7 tui3 i kong2 ¡§theng3-hau7 khah toa7-han3 e5 si5 chiah ka7 li2 kong2.¡¨ Siong7-te3 tui3 lan2 ia7 si7 an2-ni, ti7 Seng3-keng tiong sou2 ki3-chai3 e5 su7, u7 e5 lan2 thak8 liau2 boe7 beng5-pek8, chia-e5 peng3 m7-si7 sia2 m7-tioh8 a2-si7 bo5 i3-su3. Si7 hian7-chai7 lan2 boe7 thang liau2-kai2, chong2-si7 u7 chit8-jit8 Seng3 Sin5 beh hou7 lan2 liau2-kai2. Chu2 kong2: ¡§Goa2 iau2 u7 choe7-choe7 hang7 beh ka7 lin2 kong2, tok8-tok8 lin2 hian7-kim boe7 oe7 liau2-kai2, kau3 chin-li2 e5 Sin5 lai5, I beh chhoa7 lin2 beng5-pek8 it-chhe3 e5 chin-li2.¡¨ (Iok-han7 16:12,13. Tiong-bun5 e5 hoan-ek8.) Sou2-i2 hian7-chai7 lan2 thak8 Seng3-keng u7 boe7 liau2-kai2 e5 pou7-hun7, lan2 tioh8 siong-sin3. Chiau3 lan2 leng5-seng3 tiong2-chin3 e5 theng5-tou7, Seng3 Sin5 beh ban7-ban7 chhoa7 lan2 beng5-pek8 it-chhe3 e5 chin-li2. U7 e5, kiam2-chhai2 tioh8 ban7 kau3 li7-khui se3-kan i2-au7 chiah hoe7 beng5-pek8. Sou2-i2 lan2 thak8 Seng3-keng sui-jian5 u7 boe7 beng5-pek8 e5 sou2-chai7, ia7 tioh8 sin3-hok8 lai7-bin7 sou2 kong2 e5! 
  6. Seng3-keng Ki3 Hoan7 Choe7 e5 Su7-sit8, Si7 Beh Choe3 Lan2 e5 Kam3-kai3 
  U7-lang5 thak8 Seng3-keng, khoann3-kinn3 lai7-bin7 u7 ki3-chai3 Siong7-te3 e5 peh-senn3 chhoa7 se3-i5, chiu2-chui3, iah8-si7 kong2 peh8-chhat8 chiong2-chiong2 hoan7-choe7 e5 su7-sit8, chiu7 siunn7-kong2 an2-ni cho3, kann2 si7 bo5 iau3-kin2. Chhiann2 m7-thang boe7-ki3-tit, Seng3-keng ki3 chia-e5 su7, si7 beh cho3 lan2 e5 kam3-kai3, m7-si7 beh cho3 lan2 e5 bou5-iunn7. Seng3-keng m7-na7 ki3 chiah e5 hoan7-choe7 e5 heng5-ui5, ia7-u7 ki3 chia-e5 choe7 e5 kiat-ko2, si7 ui7-tioh8 beh hou7 lan2 beng5-pek8 ¡§cheng3 sim2-mih8 chiu7 siu sim2-mih8¡¨ e5 to7-li2, thang choe3 kam3-kai3 siu7 ka3-si7. Sou2-i2 m7-thang lam7-sam2 ku2 Seng3-keng tiong sou2 ki3 hoan7-choe7 e5 le7 lai5 choe3 iam-hou7 e5 oe7 lai5 hong3-chhiong3 ka-ki7 e5 su-iok8. 
